snippet.title: Knightmare Tower (Official Gameplay) by Juicy Beast Studio
snippet.description:
Here's some official gameplay footage from Knightmare Tower, the latest Juicy Beast game (previous video was still in beta)! It's not available yet, but it will be soon. The game is currently under bidding on http://www.flashgamelicense.com/

For more info, visit http://juicybeast.com/
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/juicybeast
Twitter: https://twitter.com//juicybeast
Google+: https://plus.google.com/108157607990849336850
